SELECT * FROM ab_tests;
SELECT test_name, test_description FROM ab_tests;
SELECT test_id, test_name, start_date FROM ab_tests WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT test_id, test_name, end_date FROM ab_tests WHERE end_date < '2022-12-31';
SELECT test_id, test_name, user_id, conversion_value FROM ab_tests JOIN test_results ON ab_tests.test_id = test_results.test_id WHERE is_conversion = true;
SELECT * FROM ab_tests;
SELECT test_name, test_description, start_date, end_date FROM ab_tests ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT test_id, test_name, COUNT(result_id) AS total_results FROM ab_tests LEFT JOIN test_results ON ab_tests.test_id = test_results.test_id GROUP BY test_id, test_name;
SELECT test_name, conversion_value FROM ab_tests JOIN test_results ON ab_tests.test_id = test_results.test_id WHERE is_conversion = True;
SELECT test_name, version, is_conversion FROM ab_tests JOIN test_results ON ab_tests.test_id = test_results.test_id WHERE version LIKE 'A%' AND is_conversion = True ORDER BY test_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_users;
SELECT user_id, user_email, user_age FROM website_users WHERE user_gender = 'male';
SELECT experiment_name, start_date, end_date FROM website_experiments WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, experiment_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_email, user_age, signup_date FROM website_users WHERE user_age >= 25 ORDER BY signup_date ASC;
SELECT user_id, user_email, user_age FROM website_users WHERE user_gender='Male';
SELECT user_id, user_email, user_age, signup_date FROM website_users WHERE user_age >= 25 ORDER BY signup_date DESC;

SELECT user_id, user_email, experiment_name, description FROM website_users JOIN user_interactions ON website_users.user_id = user_interactions.user_id JOIN website_experiments ON user_interactions.experiment_id = website_experiments.experiment_id;
SELECT * FROM website_users WHERE user_gender='Female' AND signup_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY signup_date ASC;

SELECT user_id, user_email, user_age, experiment_name, timestamp FROM website_users JOIN user_interactions ON website_users.user_id = user_interactions.user_id JOIN website_experiments ON user_interactions.experiment_id = website_experiments.experiment_id WHERE user_age < 30 AND timestamp > '2021-06-01';

SELECT experiment_name, start_date FROM experiment WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT username, email FROM user_data WHERE username LIKE 'user%';
SELECT experiment_id, COUNT(*) FROM page_views GROUP BY experiment_id;
SELECT user_id, experiment_id, conversion_timestamp FROM conversion_data ORDER BY user_id, conversion_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiment;
SELECT experiment_name, start_date, end_date FROM experiment ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email, registration_date FROM user_data WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT experiment_id, COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) as num_users FROM page_views GROUP BY experiment_id ORDER BY num_users DESC;

SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, conversion_timestamp FROM experiment e JOIN conversion_data c ON e.experiment_id = c.experiment_id WHERE conversion_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM Users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT username, email FROM Users WHERE registration_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT user_id, username, email, registration_date FROM Users ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Experiments WHERE start_date <= '2022-03-01' AND end_date >= '2022-03-01';
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_description, start_date FROM Experiments WHERE end_date > '2022-03-31';
SELECT * FROM Users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT username, email FROM Users WHERE registration_date > '2021-01-01';

SELECT u.username, e.experiment_name, vr.variation_name, ev.event_name FROM Users u JOIN ExperimentResults er ON u.user_id = er.user_id JOIN Experiments e ON er.experiment_id = e.experiment_id JOIN Variations vr ON er.variation_chosen = vr.variation_id JOIN Events ev ON er.conversion_event = ev.event_id;
SELECT e.experiment_id, e.experiment_name, COUNT(er.result_id) AS total_results FROM Experiments e LEFT JOIN ExperimentResults er ON e.experiment_id = er.experiment_id GROUP BY e.experiment_id;

SELECT u.username, e.experiment_name, er.result_date FROM Users u INNER JOIN ExperimentResults er ON u.user_id = er.user_id INNER JOIN Experiments e ON er.experiment_id = e.experiment_id WHERE er.result_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
